# Memory Protocol
## START of every session: READ IN ORDER
1. STATUS.md — where are we right now?
2. memory/00-project.md — what is this project?
3. memory/01-architecture.md — how is it built?
## BEFORE any architectural change: CHECK
- memory/02-decisions.md — why things are the way they are
## AFTER completing any task: UPDATE
- STATUS.md (exactly 3 lines: NOW / NEXT / BLOCKED)
- memory/02-decisions.md (only if architectural decision was made)
## SESSION LOG (only when user asks):
- memory/sessions/YYYY-MM-DD-title.md
